Knowing all of this is considered to be basic:

1️⃣ Pawn in 5th rank (bishop or central pawn)
2️⃣ Pawn in 5th rank (knight pawn)
3️⃣ Pawn in 5th rank (rook pawn)
4️⃣ Stopping a rook pawn
5️⃣ Pawn in the 4th rank
6️⃣ Pawn in the 3rd rank }
