[SetUp "1"]
[UTCDate "2019.03.13"]
[UTCTime "01:01:11"]

{ If we try to castle in this position, we can't, because the d1 square is not empty (and it's needed for the rook).

This might be confusing sometimes, as in standard chess we don't have a rook on d1, but hey, we wouldn't castle long with the queen on d1, right? It's just the same! } { [%csl Gb1,Ga1] }
1. Rd2 { After this we will be able to castle! } 1... Ke8 2. O-O-O *


