{ 🛠️ 1st rank defence ➡️Use it against a knight's pawn
🛠️ 3rd rank defence (Phillidor) ➡️Use it whenever you can
🛠️ Long-side defence ➡️Use it to prevent Lucena
🛠️ Kling and Horwitz ➡️Use it when you can't use anything else }
