{ This example is a perfect combination of the 2 techniques: time-gaining check and shoulder-charging.

White to move and win:

... }
1. Ra2+! { .
Remember to consider any check (even a lateral one) whenever the king is an ideal position to help the pawn promote.
... } 1... Kf3 2. Ra8 { Shoulder charging! } 2... e3 3. Rf8+ Ke2 4. Kg2 *


