... } { [%csl Gg6,Ge7] }
1... Qa7! { Queen on the 7th rank and king accessing to g6.
You should be familiar with the winning trick that is coming:
... } { [%csl Gg6] } 2. Kh8 { [%csl Gg6] } 2... Kg6! { .
And Black wins. } { [%csl Gg6] } *


[Event "Queen vs pawn: Bishop's pawn: winning zone against king on the right side (b)"]
