[UTCTime "18:55:46"]

{ Let's show how to win by accessing the other key square, e7:

... } { [%csl Gg6,Ge7] }
1... Qg2+ { [%csl Ge7] } 2. Kf6 (2. Kf8 { Against any other move, Ke7 stops promotion with an easy win.
The problem now for White is that there are no more Kh8 stalemate tricks, so this is also an easy win:
... } { [%csl Ge7] } 2... Qg5 3. Ke8 Qe7#) 2... Qf3+ 3. Kg7 Ke7 *


