[UTCDate "2019.05.05"]
[UTCTime "20:00:13"]

{ Apparently Black has a good blockade on d8.
But it's not enough because the bishop cantriangulate the knight into zugzwang.

... }
1. Kc7! { .
Stopping Nd6+, which was actually the only resource to draw.
... } (1. Bd5?? Nd6+ 2. Kc7 Ne8+! 3. Kc8 (3. Kc6 Kd8) 3... Nd6+ $10) (1. Bc6 { also works, since it prevents the Ne8+ trick } 1... Nd6+ 2. Kc7 { [%csl Re8][%cal Gd6e8] }) 1... Nd8 (1... Kf8 2. Bd5) 2. Bd5! { Zugzwang
Important to remember:
1) When the pawn is on the 7th rank, a passive defense usually loses to zugzwang
2) Perpetual check with the knight is the best drawing resource } *


[Event "Knight vs Bishop (wiht 1 pawn on the board): Stalemate resource"]
[Date "2019.05.05"]
[Result "*"]
[Variant "Standard"]
