Perfect! Do we draw now?...
... } { [%csl Rc1,Rd2][%cal Gc5b3] } 2... Kc3! { .
No, we're losing!
No way for the knight to stop promotion now.
... } { [%csl Rb3,Rd3][%cal Gc3b3,Gc3d3] } 3. Ne4+ Kd3 4. Nc5+ Kc4 { [%csl Rb3,Rd3][%cal Gc4b3,Gc4d3] } *


