{ We'll try to practice our recipe against the Evans Gambit, so please allow it by avoiding the Fried Liver with 3 ... Bc5 :-) }
1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. b4 Bxb4 { Exactly! The pawn must be taken. } (4... Nxb4 { Playable, but not our recipe. }) 5. c3 Be7 (5... Bd6 { Very dangerous choice. Also, not our recipe :-) }) (5... Bc5 { Very dangerous choice. Also, not our recipe :-) }) (5... Ba5 { That's a good solid option, but not our recipe :-) }) 6. d4 Na5 7. Be2 d6 8. dxe5 dxe5 9. Qa4+ c6 10. Nxe5 Nf6 { [%csl Rc3,Ra2] } *


[Event "How to survive the Fried Liver Attack: TEST: Evans with 6. Qb3"]
[Date "2019.01.10"]
