1. Kd6+ Kf6 2. Kd7 Rb1 { .
Another interesting attempt. Black decides to keep the king near the pawn and bring the rook back to deliver some checks. Unfortunately, this immediately enters a Lucena position:
... } 3. e7! { .
The pawn threatens to promote and there's only one way to avoid it, the check:
... } 3... Rd1+ 4. Ke8 { Lucena. } *


