{ This pattern is not so frequent as the DOVETAIL, but it's a pretty one.
When the king has 2 contiguous diagonal escape squares blocked, a queen can deliver checkmate with a frontal attack.

... }
1... Qf3# { [%csl Gf3,Rh4,Rh2][%cal Be5f3] } *


