{ By far the most common scenario of SWALLOW's TAIL checkmate is when the king is on the side of the board. In this case, there are no escaping squares and a frontal queen check is simply checkmate.

... } { [%cal Bd7g7] }
1. Qxg7# { [%csl Gg7][%cal Bd7g7] } *


[Event "Checkmates - Patterns with defended queen: Only one escape exists"]
[Date "2020.06.03"]
[Result "*"]
[Variant "Standard"]
[ECO "?"]
[Opening "?"]
