{ We already mentioned that pawn chains can be a trap for their own king. DOVETAIL pattern is more common, but we can find sometimes a SWALLOW's TAIL mate too, such as this one:

... } { [%csl Rf6,Rh6][%cal Bf3e4] }
1. Qe4+ { .
Diagonal check, only one escape square is free: } { [%csl Rf6,Rh6,Ge4][%cal Rf5g5,Bf3e4] } 1... Kg5 { [%csl Rf6,Rh6][%cal Bf3g4] } 2. Qg4# { [%csl Rf6,Rh6,Gg4][%cal Bf3g4] } *


