[UTCTime "18:27:18"]

{ In the previous example, there was a very unfortunate pawn chain that enabled the pattern.
Here only one pawn (as well as the side of the board) is enough to kill the king.
This pattern is very common and worthy to remember:

... }
1. Qf3+ { [%csl Gf3,Rg5][%cal Bg2f3,Rg4h4] } 1... Kh4 { [%csl Rg5][%cal Bg2h3] } 2. Qh3# { [%csl Rg5,Gh3][%cal Bg2h3] } *


