[UTCTime "15:42:22"]

{ As we know, 2 pawns separated by one file can defend each other (so Black does not lose).

But if the floating square reaches the back rank (as in this position), to be able to promote we need to force a zugzwang. Thankfully in this position, Black has moves with the king:

... } { [%cal Bb3a3,Bb3c3,Bc2c3,Bc2c1,Ba2a3,Ba2a1,Gb1a1,Gb1c1] }
1... Kh8 { zugzwang } 2. Kc2 (2. h7 Kxh7) 2... a2 { Black wins } *


[Event "Pawn endings (more than 1 pawn on the board): Protected passed pawns"]
[Date "2019.05.30"]
[Result "*"]
[Variant "Standard"]
[ECO "?"]
[Opening "?"]
