1. e4 Nc6 2. Nf3 d6 { B00 Nimzowitsch Defense: Williams Variation. Still the most popular move. } 3. d4 Bg4 4. Be3 Nf6 5. Nc3 e6 6. h3 Bh5 7. Bd3?! { (0.97 → 0.36) Inaccuracy. Best move was d5. } (7. d5 exd5 8. exd5 Ne5 9. g4 Bg6 10. g5 Nxf3+ 11. Qxf3 Bh5 12. Qf4 Nd7 13. Be2 Bxe2) 7... Be7?! { (0.36 → 0.92) Inaccuracy. Best move was d5. } (7... d5) 8. a3?! { (0.92 → 0.40) Inaccuracy. Best move was g4. } (8. g4 Bg6 9. g5 Nh5 10. d5 Nb4 11. Be2 exd5 12. a3 dxe4 13. Nd4 Bxg5 14. axb4 Bxe3) 8... Bg6 9. Qe2 O-O 10. g4?! { (0.60 → 0.00) Inaccuracy. Best move was O-O. } (10. O-O a6) 10... d5 11. e5 Bxd3 12. Qxd3 Ne8?! { (-0.05 → 0.92) Inaccuracy. Best move was Nd7. } (12... Nd7) 13. g5 g6 14. h4 Ng7 15. Nh2 Nf5 16. Ng4 Kg7?! { (0.84 → 1.61) Inaccuracy. Best move was h5. } (16... h5 17. gxh6 Bxh4 18. O-O-O Kh7 19. Kb1 Be7 20. Ne2 Nb8 21. Ng3 Nd7 22. Nxf5 gxf5 23. Rdg1) 17. Nf6?! { (1.61 → 0.63) Inaccuracy. Best move was O-O-O. } (17. O-O-O) 17... Rh8? { (0.63 → 2.09) Mistake. Best move was h5. } (17... h5) 18. h5 h6 19. hxg6? { (1.84 → 0.00) Mistake. Best move was O-O-O. } (19. O-O-O) 19... fxg6? { (0.00 → 2.23) Mistake. Best move was hxg5. } (19... hxg5 20. Rxh8 Qxh8 21. O-O-O Bxf6 22. exf6+ Kxf6 23. gxf7 Qh5 24. Rg1 Kxf7 25. Nxd5 Rd8 26. Nxc7) 20. gxh6+ Nxh6?? { (2.31 → 6.67) Blunder. Best move was Kf7. } (20... Kf7 21. Ng4 Ke8 22. O-O-O Kd7 23. Kb1 Rh7 24. Ne2 Qg8 25. Qd2 g5 26. Ng3 Qg6 27. Nh5) 21. Rg1? { (6.67 → 3.78) Mistake. Best move was Rxh6. } (21. Rxh6 Rxh6 22. Bxh6+ Kf7 23. Bg5 Rb8 24. O-O-O Qh8 25. Qf3 Bxf6 26. exf6 Rd8 27. Ne2 Qg8) 21... Nf5 22. Ncxd5 Bxf6 23. Nxf6 Ncxd4?! { (4.17 → 4.79) Inaccuracy. Best move was Nce7. } (23... Nce7) 24. O-O-O c5 25. Qc4? { (4.51 → 2.94) Mistake. Best move was Qe4. } (25. Qe4 Qc7 26. Kb1 Rad8 27. Qg4 Qf7 28. Bg5 Rh2 29. Ne4 Rc8 30. c3 Nb3 31. Bf6+ Kf8) 25... b5?? { (2.94 → 6.29) Blunder. Best move was Qb6. } (25... Qb6 26. Ne4) 26. Qxc5 Rc8 27. Qxa7+ Rc7 28. Bh6+?? { (5.48 → -1.94) Blunder. Best move was Rxd4. } (28. Rxd4) 28... Kf7 29. Qa6 Rxc2+?! { (-1.86 → -1.23) Inaccuracy. Best move was Rxh6. } (29... Rxh6 30. Kb1 Qb8 31. Ne4 Ra7 32. Nd6+ Kf8 33. Qc8+ Qxc8 34. Nxc8 Rc7 35. Nd6 Nf3 36. Rg4) 30. Kb1 Rxh6 31. Ne4? { (-1.41 → -2.57) Mistake. Best move was Rc1. } (31. Rc1 Rxc1+ 32. Rxc1 Ne7 33. Qb7 Rh4 34. Ne4 Rh5 35. Nd6+ Kg8 36. Rc7 Ndc6 37. Rxc6 Nxc6) 31... Qc7 32. Nd6+?! { (-2.57 → -3.18) Inaccuracy. Best move was Rc1. } (32. Rc1 Rxc1+ 33. Rxc1 Qxe5 34. Re1 Qc7 35. Ng5+ Kf6 36. Nxe6 Qc2+ 37. Ka1 Qc6 38. Qxc6 Nxc6) 32... Nxd6 33. exd6?? { White resigns. } { (-3.05 → Mate in 4) Checkmate is now unavoidable. Best move was Rxd4. } (33. Rxd4 Re2 34. Ka1 Nf5 35. Rb4 Rxe5 36. Rxb5 Rxb5 37. Qxb5 Rh2 38. Rd1 Qf4 39. Qb7+ Kf6) 33... Rxb2+ 34. Ka1 Ra2+ 35. Kxa2 Qc2+ 36. Ka1 Nb3# 0-1


